  "text": "In Table 1 , some sample dead codes are given [CITATION_1] , which are actually useless instructions and semantically equivalent to no operation (NOP). None of the operation samples, in Table 1 , changes value of the register. Adding a value 0 to a register or a variable, transferring a register value to itself, a logical OR operation of register or variable with a 0 and a logical AND operation of a register or variable with a same length register or variable filled by binary value 1, or immediate constant -1 will not affect on the execution process.",
